            "reset": "<p>The mannequins freeze in place as soon as there is no life within the room, resetting the haunt.</p>",
            "routine": "<p>(9 actions) Each of the mannequins uses three of the haunt's actions on each turn, and the haunt loses three actions each turn for every disabled or destroyed mannequin. Each mannequin uses its first action to Stride up to 15 feet and spends its remaining two actions making mannequin fist or flung trinket Strikes. Each mannequin has its own separate multiple attack penalty.</p>"
